name: Worthless billions #2
description: This is a series of characters that have made billions during the pandemic, increasing their ‘worth’, for whatever that means. As of today, April 16th, 2021, Jeff Bezos’ net worth is 197.8 billion USD according to Forbes.   19 pieces available, each one representing one hundred billion of this worth, all pieces that are not sold within the 1-hour 9-minute timeframe will be burned and will be just as meaningless as Bezos’ intangible billions.  560px · 178F
